Hey Ernest!

     It's Ryan, from West Campus. I was listening to NIN Pretty Hate
Machine earlier and it reminded me of you. I was happy to see your website
is still up, it's good that you didn't stop creating things.

    How has everything been? I'm sorry that I fell out of contact with you;
I have been struggling with various things, and I became sort of reclusive.
I'd love to catch up sometime, whether it be online or even in person. You
were always really funny and not afraid to say what was on your mind.

   I look forward to hearing from you man.

